short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Volo Safe extension, built on Sui blockchain

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A utility extension to the Volo wallet that enables seamless, secure, and efficient management of digital assets. Built on the innovative Sui network, It offers a simple, yet powerful solution for connecting to other applications like Suiswap or any other application requiring a wallet.
